{"tid":742773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰開打，禁毒合作終止，中國繼續向美輸出鴉片類藥物","createTime":"2018-07-15T00:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T17:15:41.000Z","uid":141151,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"99fe98cef06a2f660c731dc7bb91c301715e9da4","tid":742773,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:06:59.000Z","msg":"貿易戰開打，禁毒合作終止，中國繼續向美輸出鴉片類藥物<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20180714-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E9%96%8B%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%90%91%E7%BE%8E%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E9%B4%89%E7%89%87%E9%A1%9E%E8%97%A5%E7%89%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20180714-%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2589%2593%25EF%25BC%258C%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25AD%25A2%25EF%25BC%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%25B4%2589%25E7%2589%2587%25E9%25A1%259E%25E8%2597%25A5%25E7%2589%25A9&d=qbdn2e%2BZltgxhYmaxHhzdbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cb7b73bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20180714-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E9%96%8B%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%90%91%E7%BE%8E%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E9%B4%89%E7%89%87%E9%A1%9E%E8%97%A5%E7%89%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n美國力圖遏止鴉片類藥物日益泛濫的努力，將在特朗普總統對中國發動貿易戰之後付諸東流。據《凱澤健康新聞》（Kaiser Health News）報道，美中貿易戰致使雙方一些與貿易無關的議題合作喊停，特別是針對芬太尼（fentanyl）等危險鴉片類藥物從中國輸入美國的問題。<br />\n<br />\n美國的大部分芬太尼和其他鴉片類藥物來自中國。芬太尼效力比海洛因強50倍，比嗎啡強100倍。據美國疾病控制及預防中心（CDC）的一份報告顯示，鴉片類藥物易已導致300萬美國人嗑藥上癮，去年6萬4千人死亡。雖然中國官員矢口否認向美國輸出鴉片類藥物，但過去曾努力與美國政府合作控制芬太尼向美國輸出。<br />\n<br />\n美國緝毒署（DEA）代理署長帕特森（Robert Patterson）於3月在國會發表一份聲明，將美國和中國緝毒機構之間的合作關係描述為：一個重要的雙邊機制，以解決非法芬太尼和其他合成藥物輸入美國。但緝毒署探員主任希金斯（Jeffrey Higgins）近日表示，美中貿易戰開打，已傳聞中國官員說：他們將不再與美國合作控制這些鴉片類藥物。<br />\n<br />\n專家表示，如果特朗普繼續對中國加征關稅，美中的禁毒合作可能會完全終止，中國方面將放任鴉片類藥物繼續輸出美國。"},{"pid":"9560263bd4f966c0bb8fd0fde4ee30ce6e76995d","tid":742773,"uid":51937,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:11:04.000Z","msg":"發爛渣了"},{"pid":"3bdeb80f804fc592ffe5f4881091e0fdd97690b3","tid":742773,"uid":76216,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:11:46.000Z","msg":"AA+"},{"pid":"b733b9450eeca9280aef0df1382eefd50c7170c3","tid":742773,"uid":113626,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:13:18.000Z","msg":"鄰國成日話咩自己另世界走向和平<br />\n一有利益衝突就現形 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2947e921872612025428c33382e54b048440bc8","tid":742773,"uid":85168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"侵侵根本唔多理 war on drugs，上任後直情諗過 shut down ONDCP"},{"pid":"35f24ca3ba0a676fd84861cecbbb9aad7feda612","tid":742773,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:36:17.000Z","msg":"既然貿易戰侵侵會死<br />\n你就由得佢啦"},{"pid":"a5bccb77367d4824952442798a5046486d2fad2b","tid":742773,"uid":193555,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:40:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b7c57518e48363d6d5f5bebd211b201a5a4bf10","tid":742773,"uid":90704,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:41:53.000Z","msg":"本來口頭幫你控制輸出<br />\n而家激嬲共產黨 口頭都唔幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6f1ca3b8686988cee5588729730010bc5f79a5","tid":742773,"uid":82749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:42:53.000Z","msg":"美國咁多毒撚<br />\n禁毒is on9"},{"pid":"7da241dabf373e9b27560774b4454ac6595285e0","tid":742773,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T00:47:11.000Z","msg":"鴉片戰爭?<img src=\"/assets/